Author: Asteria Nocturna
Name: Divination.AetheryteLinkInChat
Punchline: Quick teleport for mob hunts and treasure hunts!
Description: Display a teleport link to the nearest aetherite for the map link from the in-game chat. Type /alic to configure the plugin.
Changelog:
dd8161f: Memorize player's world
28680e8: add option to hide UI in duty
88e2314: add open map button
52ac778: I forgot to add it to the settings UI...
dbc33c1: add option to line-break before links
4c515c4: we should use string.Join instead of Object.ToString...
07ded97: add option to ignore some aetherytes
e2b6c31: spawn_location does not contain zoneId
f85deb9: add option to skip pending spawn reports
39df878: replace Boxed letters with alphabets
498a949: support new zoneId format (Close #653)
fbaa3b6: receive home DC mobs when you are traveling to Oceania DC
54e6dbb: return true if LocalPlayer cannot be obtained
ded2dd1: remove default initializer
0d1cceb: no longer needed
54fb863: add Quest notification on teleport
3d37154: remove cache behavior
11eaf1d: I don't use Rider anymore
834c2aa: show notification when current world/DC unavailable

e.g. while you are logging in
b4b84d6: improve Active Mobs appearance
33b5ab2: add AetheryteLinkInChat.Teleport IPC
f923c37: init CancellationTokenSource
da025af: cleaning task
a9fff10: add Horoscope project
ac00690: fix for Faloop embed data structure
646ef3c: Merge branch 'master' of ssh://github.com/SlashNephy/Divination
1b5706f: Merge pull request #649 from Uriei/master

Ignore text inside map link when looking for world name
bc149dc: include oceania DC option
e39f14a: Ignore text inside map link when looking for world name

This was causing issue with maps like Ultima Thule, detecting it was always in the Ultima japan world.
80f87e4: wait before world traveling
